fields.value: The Morphology of First-Person Object Forms of Directional Verbs in American Sign Language

dsDescriptionValue.value: The dataset contains the stimuli used for eliciting directional verbs in American Sign Language (ASL). The stimuli consists of short video clips of a middle-aged Caucasian-American woman demonstrating the verbs in isolation.
